Package: CEAforests
Type: Package
Title: Tree-based heterogenous cost-effectiveness and policy learning with individual-level data (beta)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Carl Bonander
Maintainer: Carl Bonander <carl.bonander@gu.se>
Description: This package includes wrappers for estimating causal (or instrumental) causal forests and policy decision trees in cost-effectiveness analyses with individual-level data from randomized trials or observational studies. The core functionality relies on the grf and policytree packages.
Imports: grf, ggplot2, cowplot, tableone, boot, sandwich, stats, policytree
Suggests: mgcv, DiagrammeR
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
